privacy.collect_text:
We collect the following data:
- Full name, phone number, and email address;
- Identity documents and certificates confirming eligibility for assistance;
- Uploaded photos or videos related to your request;
- Technical data such as IP address, browser, and language;
- Payment details related to donations (not including card numbers).

privacy.usage_text:
We use data only for platform operation:
- Verifying user identity using AI technologies;
- Publishing support requests and managing donations;
- Sending important updates and notifications;
- Performing analytics to detect fraud and improve quality;
- Meeting legal obligations in Kazakhstan.

privacy.protect_text:
Your information is protected using:
- Encrypted connections (SSL);
- Secure servers with limited access;
- Regular internal security audits;
- Fully automated AI-powered document verification.

privacy.rights_text:
You have the right to:
- Request deletion or correction of your personal data;
- Withdraw your consent at any time;
- Request a copy of your stored data;
- File a complaint if you believe your data was misused.

terms.user_rules_text:
As a user, you agree to:
- Provide true and complete information in your requests;
- Not post fraudulent, misleading, or spam content;
- Respect the community and refrain from offensive behavior;
- Avoid commercial use without written consent.

terms.responsibility_text:
We do our best to moderate content but do not guarantee:
- That every request will be published or supported;
- That assistance will be received;
- We may remove any post that violates rules or laws.
